 Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131712238,imgsize-100638.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kai Cenat’s Streamer University event draws massive crowds and chaos in NYC]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131712134.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kai Cenat's Streamer University event in New York City saw huge crowds. Aspiring content creators gathered for the free event. Many fans waited overnight for a chance to apply. Police managed the large turnout. This event is the first of three planned by Cenat. The massive response shows the popularity of Cenat and his initiative.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kai-cenats-streamer-university-event-draws-massive-crowds-and-chaos-in-nyc/articleshow/131712134.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kai-cenats-streamer-university-event-draws-massive-crowds-and-chaos-in-nyc/articleshow/131712134.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-14T01:10:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131712129,imgsize-1185623.cms"/></item></channel></rss>